# rag-salesforce-architect

RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) system designed with an **enterprise/architect mindset** to answer questions about
Salesforce technical documentation (Apex, Flows, ADRs, Confluence exports, PDFs).

## Goals
- Ingest technical docs (PDF/MD/TXT)
- Chunk + embed
- Store vectors in **FAISS (local)**
- Retrieve evidence and generate answers **grounded with citations**
- Expose a minimal **FastAPI** service
- Include evaluation to reduce hallucinations

## Quickstart (local)

### 1) Setup
```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows PowerShell:
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
python -m pip install -U pip
python -m pip install -e .[dev]
